Svc types
========

	1. ClusterIP: it will expose the app within the cluster , it is for internal access.
	2. NodePort:- it will expose  the application on a static port on each nodes ip.

	Ø The app accessible externally but only on specific ports between 30000 to 32767

When to use:
===========

	Ø It is for only test 


	3. LoadBalancer:- it will expose the app within the cluster and out side the cluster by giving external ip add without any port limitations
	Ø It is a paid not free


	4. ExnternalName:
 ================


